dct_title_s: Asia-Pacific LNG map / Petroleum Economist Cartographic ; produced by Petroleum Economist Limited, a division of Euromoney Global Ltd in association with King & Spalding ; designed by K. Fuller and P. Bush
dct_description_sm: Relief and depths shown by shading. "Published December 2015" Shows gas fields, gas pipelines, export plants, import terminals. Accompanies: Petroleum economist, v.83, no.1, February 2016. Includes statistical charts and graphs, 4 inset maps, and 1 ancillary map.
